OL,3,CBody of teenager recovered from pond
OL,4,Cafter major search
OL,6,FThe body of a teenage boy has been
OL,7,Frecovered from a pond in Kent
OL,8,Ffollowing a major search operation in
OL,9,Fthe area.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to
OL,12,Freports of concerns for a swimmer in
OL,13,Fthe Galley Hill Road area of
OL,14,FSwanscombe on Wednesday afternoon.
OL,16,FKent Police said its officers attended
OL,17,Fwith the Kent Fire and Rescue Service
OL,18,Fand the South East Coast Ambulance
OL,19,FService.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
