OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1779987954
OL,3,CBody of teenager recovered from pond
OL,4,Cafter major search
OL,6,FThe boy's death is not being treated
OL,7,Fas suspicious at this time, the force
OL,8,Fsaid.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FIt comes after seven children and two
OL,16,Fadults drowned over the past week amid
OL,17,Fsoaring temperatures across the UK.
OL,19,FThe deaths included a teenage boy,
OL,20,Fwhose body was pulled from a lake near
OL,21,FBlackwater, in Hampshire.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
