OL,3,CBody of teenager recovered from pond
OL,4,Cafter major search
OL,6,FSo far, those reported to have died in
OL,7,Fwater incidents are:
OL,9,FIt's prompted a warning from the Royal
OL,10,FLife Saving Society to "stop and
OL,11,Fthink" before getting into the water.
OL,13,FThe organisation noted that "warmer
OL,14,Fweather unfortunately correlates to an
OL,15,Fincrease in accidental drownings" and
OL,16,Fthat despite warmer air, "water
OL,17,Ftemperatures remain very cold".
